{"tid":1125280,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"架車入面有文件唔好開篷黎揸 屌","createTime":"2019-04-25T14:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T15:07:20.000Z","uid":171273,"like":9,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ca99ee5f99f4a753a60855dab84b86a69f72abef","tid":1125280,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:50:06.000Z","msg":"話說我係沙田區某酒店做泊車仔<br />\n<br />\n平時有客黎食野/check in都會幫手泊<br />\n<br />\n今晚有個西裝友一個人揸部z4黎比左一舊水tip屎我幫手泊車<br />\n<br />\n咁我地泊車仔平時有靚車都會揸上吐露港公路飛兩轉係不明文規矩黎<br />\n<br />\n有部棍波寶馬我緊係貪玩點都玩兩手啦<br />\n<br />\n揸揸下我諗住有得開篷唔好嘥 開黎威下<br />\n<br />\n點知一開篷就奶野<br />\n<br />\n佢副座有疊文件無夾好 一吹就吹哂起身 <br />\n<br />\n應該吹散左d係條路到<br />\n<br />\n我即刻禁實佢疊野閂返個篷 <br />\n<br />\n返左轉頭返酒店扮無事發生<br />\n<br />\n個客攞返車走左都無投訴 希望小事一樁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d7e0ea3f4c8d4dd84fb52d27f70cac0f58d3e8","tid":1125280,"uid":210280,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:51:13.000Z","msg":"上黎自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e60b84e3a59df8f3c7f589aaf4c1a97255d66f7c","tid":1125280,"uid":249562,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:52:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27892e0f7566f403a5fc5c1549af813881e5a832","tid":1125280,"uid":74171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:55:23.000Z","msg":"許志安冇歌唱，宜家連泊車都做埋？"},{"pid":"60a352894335a100335c117cfecd6a1251e8fcf6","tid":1125280,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b2d7e0ea3f4c8d4dd84fb52d27f70cac0f58d3e8","tid":1125280,"uid":210280,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:51:13.000Z","msg":"上黎自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:57:08.000Z","msg":"日期地點有改過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae12da93f1e2f73574ebd071bbed6883a36009b","tid":1125280,"uid":42852,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:58:53.000Z","msg":"無事嘅，你跌咗我份文件咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾你老母我咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f53f0c7f956b35b5c108a2ff898bb3ad4a9cf9","tid":1125280,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:00:28.000Z","msg":"原來係你，搞到我唔見左單生意"},{"pid":"0860a70b0203e26bfabb0128f3bd2f310465c547","tid":1125280,"uid":232605,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:01:11.000Z","msg":"原來係你，今次仆街啦你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n玩你咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(認真) 人地走咗無投訴 可能未發覺咋<br />\n計我話泊完架車就算啦, 如果架車有咩損傷入你數就唔好啦"},{"pid":"65b8980b5ce72db0a148b878d454c6c47c2a9729","tid":1125280,"uid":249562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:01:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5603aa4a685c6fa5f66b4dc814e9eb9a0df77245","tid":1125280,"uid":249562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:02:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d1805108dbd78f7b43bead0bb763d39435d1305","tid":1125280,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:03:01.000Z","msg":"你聽日唔洗返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9436a0705bf687c2c883435c7f97cbcbb483d80","tid":1125280,"uid":249562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:03:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a456baa7c791b030a3170a7c9cc3049f172d4b5","tid":1125280,"uid":249562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:03:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1783221520cb4512051b7e54f69259c880f0fac7","tid":1125280,"uid":249562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-2